{"tid":2309540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網嗆「斬殺蔡英文」 台灣30歲男子觸危害安全被逮","createTime":"2020-12-02T15:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T15:30:08.000Z","uid":70331,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"56654a4b0d1b2910cbb2c26fb1591578738b7b37","tid":2309540,"uid":70331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CrvWOpNO5EI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCrvWOpNO5EI&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=b01e9ea8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CrvWOpNO5EI</a><br />\n<br />\n上網留言得當心！台南有一名30歲的男子，在網路論壇嗆聲要「斬殺蔡英文」，網友震驚，截圖檢舉，刑事局偵八隊員警將他約談到案，他說，自己長期服用安眠藥，本來要打「斬殺蔡瑁」，卻在打了蔡字之後，手機自動跳出「英文」兩字，他沒留意就PO上網了，現在，還是得依危害安全等罪嫌送辦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201806/744275223e1d208556565321f80275db.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201806%2F744275223e1d208556565321f80275db.JPG&h=634e2844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201806/96c6a213b87832bf72ad6c4919d06a6b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201806%2F96c6a213b87832bf72ad6c4919d06a6b.JPG&h=128dfa90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b402c41190b7b5530375a46ca68fd9c611e6ab4a","tid":2309540,"uid":76216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:19:14.000Z","msg":"斬殺蔡瑁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3a325e6fddf4dd3bf4a4ed61232db927d64e65","tid":2309540,"uid":209890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:20:47.000Z","msg":"蔡瑁<br />\n蔡瑁，字德珪，荊州南郡襄陽人，東漢末期名族人物，南郡大士蔡諷之子，劉表繼妻蔡氏之兄。<br />\n逝世： 西元 208 年 10 月"},{"pid":"17759e1b21f6eb6ef38e663838d73ab0239457c6","tid":2309540,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:26:01.000Z","msg":"兜得唔差"},{"pi